POD2::IT version 0.05
=====================

POD2::IT - Italian translation of Perl core documentation

See 'perldoc POD2::IT' for more info

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module doen't requires other modules and libraries

